imdb.plot outline: From Austin, TX comes a comedic web series that follows the platonic relationship between an older man and a younger woman whom, through a series of events thrown at them by the universe, live together as roommates. It's the Woodstock Generation versus the Millennials and they soon find out that they both have something to learn from each other.
imdb.title: Paul and Pauline
